quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  29,1,"alm: sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqttaet fi 'awal surat albqrt"
  29,2,"azann alnaas 'iidh qalu: amna, 'ana allah ytrkhm bila abtla' wala akhtbar?"
  29,3,"wlqd ftnna aladhin min qablihim min al'umam wakhtbrnahm, mmn 'arsalna 'iilayhim rslna, flyelmnn allah elmana zahrana llkhlq sidq alsaadiqin fi 'iymanhm, wakadhab alkadhbyn; liamiz kll fariq min alakhr"
  29,4,"bl aznn aladhin yaemalun almeasy min shirk wghyrh 'ana yejzwna, fyfwtwna bi'anfusihim fala naqdir elyhm? bis hkmhm aldhy yahkumun bh"
  29,5,"man kan yarju liqa' allh, wytme fi thwabh, fa'iina 'ajal allah aladhi ajjalh lbeth khalaqah lljza' waleiqab lat qrybana, wahu alsamie llaqwal, alealim balafeal"
  29,6,"wmn jahad fi sabil 'iiela' kalimat allah teala, wajahad nafsih bhmlha ealaa altaet, fa'iinama yujahid lnfsh; li'anah yafeal dhlk abtigha' althawab ealaa jhadh. 'iina allah laghaniun ean 'aemal jmye khlqh, lah almulk walkhlq walamr"
  29,7,"waldhyn sddaqu allah wrswlh, waeamiluu alsaalihat lnmhwnn eanhum khtyyathm, wlnthybnnahm ealaa 'aemalihim alsalht 'ahsan ma kanuu yemlwn"
  29,8,"wwsyna al'iinsan biwalidayh 'ana ybrhma, wyhsn 'ilyhma bialqawl waleml, wa'iin jahadak -ayha al'insan- ealaa 'an tushrik maei fi ebadty, fala tmtthl amrhma. wylhq bitalab al'ishrak ballh, sayr almeasy, fala taeat lmkhlwq kaynana man kan fi mesyt allah sbhanh, kama thabat dhlk ean rasul allah salaa allah ealayh wslm. 'ily masirakum yawm alqyamt, fakhbrkm bima kuntum taemalun fi aldunya min salih al'aemal wsyyha, wajazykm elyha"
  29,9,"waldhyn sddaqu allah warasulah waeamiluu alsaalihat min alaemal, lanudkhilanahum aljanat fi jumlatan eibad allah alsalhyn"
  29,10,"wmn alnaas min yqwl: amanaa ballh, fa'iidha adhah almushrikun jze min edhabhm wadhahm, kama yjze min eadhab allah wala ysbr ealaa aladhyat mnh, fartdd ean 'iymanh, walayin ja' nasr min rabik -ayha alrswl- li'ahl al'iiman bih lyqwlann hwla' almrtdwn ean 'iymanhm: 'inna kunaa maeakum -ayha almwmnwn- nnsrkm ealaa aedaykm, 'awalays allah bi'aelam min kuli ahd bima fi sudur jmye khlqh?"
  29,11,"wlyelmnn allah elmana zahrana llkhlq aladhin sddaqu allah warasulah waeamiluu bshreh, wlyelmnn almnafqyn; liamiz kl fariq min alakhr"
  29,12,"waqal aladhin jahaduu whdanyt allah min qrysh, walam yuminuu bweyd allah wwedh, liladhin sddaqu allah minhum waeamiluu bshreh: autrukuu din mhmd, watabaeuu dynna, fa'iinaa natahamal atham khtayakm, wlysu bihamilin min athamhm min shy', 'iinahum lakadhibun fima qalu"
  29,13,"wlyhmlann hwla' almushrikun 'awzar 'anfusahum wathamha, wawzar man 'adaluu wsddu ean sabil allah mae awzarhm, dun 'an yunqas min 'awzar tabeyhm shy', wlyusalunn yawm alqiamat eamaa kanuu ykhtlqwnh min alakadhyb"
  29,14,"wlqd 'arsalna nwhana 'iilaa qawmih famakath fihim 'alf sanat 'iilaa khamsin eamana, yadeuhum 'iilaa altwhyd wayanhahum ean alshrk, falam yastajibuu lh, fahlkhm allah baltwfan, wahum zalimun lanfshm bikufrihim wtghyanhm"
  29,15,"fanjyna nwhana wman tabieah mmn kan maeah fi alsfynt, wajaealna dhlk eibratan wezt llealmyn"
  29,16,"wadhkr -ayha alrswl- 'iibrahim ealayh alslam hin daea qwmh: 'ana akhlsu alebadt lilah whdh, wataquu skhth bi'ada' fraydh wajtnab measyh, dhlkm khayr lkm, 'iin kuntum taelamun ma hu khayr lakum mimaa hu sharun lkm"
  29,17,"ma taebudun -ayha alqwm- min dun allah 'iilaa asnamana, wtftrwn kdhbana btsmytkm 'iyaha alht, 'inn awthankm alty tebdwnha min dun allah la tuqadar 'ana trzqkm shyyana, faltamisuu eind allah alrizq la min eind awthankm, wa'akhlasuu lah alebadt walshukr ealaa rizqah 'iyakm, 'iilaa allah turddun min baed mmatkm, fyjazykm ealaa ma emltm"
  29,18,"w'in tkdhdhibu - 'ayuha alnas- rasulina mhmdana salaa allah ealayh wasalam fima daeakum 'iilayh min eibadat allah whdh, faqad kadhabat jamaeat min qablikum rslha fima dethm 'iilayh min alhq, fhl bihim sakhit allh, wama ealaa alrraswl muhamad 'iilaa 'an yblghkm ean allah risalatah albalagh alwadh, waqad faeal"
  29,19,"'awalam yaelam hwla' kayf yunashiy allah alkhalq min aledm, thuma yueiduh min baed fnayh, kama bada'ah 'awal marat khlqana jdydana, la ytedhr ealayh dhlk? 'iina dhlk ealaa allah ysyr, kama kan ysyrana ealayh 'inshawh"
  29,20,"ql -ayha alrswl- lmnkry albaeth baed almmat: siruu fi alard, fanzuruu kayf 'ansha allah alkhlq, walam ytedhr ealayh 'inshawh mbtdaan? fkdhlk la ytedhr ealayh 'iieadat 'inshayh alnash'at alakhr. 'iina allah ealaa kl shay' qdyr, la yejzh shay' aradh"
  29,21,"yedhb man yasha' min khalaqah ealaa ma aslf min jrmh fi 'ayaam hyath, wayarham man yasha' minhum mmn tab waman waeamil salhana, wa'iilayh trjewn, fyjazykm bima emltm"
  29,22,"wma 'antum -ayha alnas- bmejzy allah fi al'ard wala fi alsama' 'iin esytmwh, wama kan lakum min dun allah min wly yali amwrkm, wala nasir yansurukum min allah 'iin 'arad bikum sw'ana"
  29,23,"waldhyn jahaduu hujj allah wankru adlth, wlqa'h yawm alqyamt, 'uwlayik lays lahum mtme fi rahmati lamma eaynu ma 'ueidd lahum min aledhab, wawlyk lahum eadhab mulim mwje"
  29,24,"flm yakun jawab qawm 'iibrahim lah 'iilaa 'an qal bedhm lbed: aqtuluh 'aw hrriqwh balnar, fa'alquh fyha, fa'anjah allah mnha, wajaealaha ealayh brdana wslamana, 'iina fi 'injayna li'iibrahim min alnaar ladlt whjjana liqawm ysddiqwn allah wayaemalun bshreh"
  29,25,"wqal 'iibrahim lqwmh: ya qawm 'iinama eabadtum min dun allah alihatan batlt, atkhdhtmwha mawadat baynikum fi alhayat aldnya, tthabwn ealaa ebadtha, wttwadwn ealaa khdmtha, thuma yawm alqyamt, ytbra baedukum min bed, wayalean baedukum bedana, wmsyrkm jmyeana alnar, walays lakum nasir yamnaekum min dkhwlha"